{"tid":2248073,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"日本導演拍港抗爭　《香港画》奪「札幌國際短片節」最佳紀錄片","createTime":"2020-10-18T10:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T22:54:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5309a7ace859e3e535224b0bb7a56b70d30185","tid":2248073,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"日本電影導演堀井威久麿拍攝香港抗爭，製成紀錄片《香港画 / Montage of Hong Kong》，於該國的<strong><span class=\"red\">第 15 屆「札幌國際短片節（札幌国際短編映画祭）」(<a href=\"https://sapporoshortfest.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsapporoshortfest.jp%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=3d8deab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sapporoshortfest.jp/</a>) 獲最佳紀錄片獎。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n該作早前已於另一電影節「門真國際電影節」獲優秀賞。<br />\n<br />\n日本電影導演堀井威久麿 (Ikuma Horii) 去年曾親身來港，記錄香港抗爭，拍成作品《香港画 / Montage of Hong Kong》。片長 28 分鐘的作品主要記錄香港年輕人在這一年間，因甚麼緣故走上街頭。參與製作者亦包括<strong><span class=\"red\">日本香港抗爭團隊 Stand with Hong Kong at JPN (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106136324125783/posts/330091745063572/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106136324125783%2Fposts%2F330091745063572%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=2822b68b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106136324125783/posts/330091745063572/</a>) 的成員。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">堀井威久麿生於 1981 年，自學成獨立影片製作人。他在 facebook (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2957308127680972&amp;set=a.268626979882447&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D2957308127680972%26set%3Da.268626979882447%26type%3D3&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=c317ccc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=2957308127680972&amp;set=a.268626979882447&amp;type=3</a>) 表示</span></strong>，希望作品今後能繼續在日本國內和海外放映。他說，近距離接觸追求自由的年輕人，讓他感受到被「長大成人後或許失去了的甚麼」撼動內心。他認為，香港民主抗爭在肺炎後數十年仍會繼續擴大，這抗爭背後是中國政治體制無可避免的問題，與日本、台灣，以至越南、菲律賓等東亞諸國均有關係。<br />\n<br />\n今年已是「札幌國際短編電影節」第 15 屆舉行，該電影節共收到來自 108 個國家共 3873 部作品，最終選出 34 國共 102 部作品展出，包括《香港画》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LUJAKvcEQt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLUJAKvcEQt0&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=9eb83b6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LUJAKvcEQt0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%8B%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%BB-%E5%A5%AA-%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E7%AF%80-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25BB-%25E5%25A5%25AA-%25E6%259C%25AD%25E5%25B9%258C%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=fd8f11dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2594%25BB-%25E5%25A5%25AA-%25E6%259C%25AD%25E5%25B9%258C%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587%2F&h=7d9df423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%8B%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%BB-%E5%A5%AA-%E6%9C%AD%E5%B9%8C%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E7%AF%80-%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87/</a>"},{"pid":"4b15a5402f35c0f980da8766f205c2666fa8f6e2","tid":2248073,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c0316856208646a6bc63949c91cdadcecfa7cd","tid":2248073,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b15a5402f35c0f980da8766f205c2666fa8f6e2","tid":2248073,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36770968fda7a60adc866ace0c161fe9fa2cf02a","tid":2248073,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f21812d96ea1343afcf411020bf8766f0da78e","tid":2248073,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g